data.value: Confit de canard; is the name given to the duck leg prepared without using any oil other than its own oil. Long-cooked food; salt, garlic, thyme and other spices on request, and the addition of aroma wins and more than a day to wait for the consistency. After the meal is prepared and its consistency is served with fried or grilled potatoes and onions.
